
DA, quæsumus, omnípotens Deus: ut, sancti Joánnis Confessóris exémplo in sciéntia Sanctórum proficiéntes, atque áliis misericórdiam exhibéntes; ejus méritis, indulgéntiam apud te consequámur. Per Dóminum.
GRANT, we beseech thee, O almighty God, that, after the example of thy holy Confessor John, making progress in the science of the Saints and showing mercy to others; we may, by his merits, ourselves obtain pardon from thee. Through our Lord.
